Visit Sussex

A leading research institution, located in the beautiful and scenic South Downs National Park, what better place to study than The University of Sussex. From scientific discovery to global policy, from student welfare to career development, Sussex innovates and takes a lead. There are so many reasons to visit Sussex.

Beautiful and Scenic

Sussex campus is located in the South Downs National park and offers stunning views of the rolling hills and beautiful green spaces.

Management, Staff and Student Partnership

Academia is as thriving as it has always been as exemplified by the passionate lecturers at Sussex

Good to know!

Sussex contributes to open science by paying to publish in big-name journals and also paying to access them! For example, access to articles such as Fortunato and Galassi (2021) are included in my tuition fee!

Great Value Food

Sussex offers many food options that anyone would be envious of.

And ran a T test on the data:

Code 
colnames(df)[3] <- "university_love"
df$University <- as.factor(df$University)
t.test(university_love~University, data=df)

    Welch Two Sample t-test
